Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' for cases that eventually reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to transition to any subsequent activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases starting with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average waiting time to transition from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time cases spend in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before reaching 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor for cases where activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved' in comparison to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average time for a case to move from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a case to move from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' Cycle Time in comparison to 'Accepted + Wait' Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
